metadata.name: Woman Looking Out to Sea #1
metadata.description:
I took this photo in Keflav√≠k, Iceland while out for a walk on the last morning of my 3-month solo trip. 

Like the photographed rock statue, I found myself gazing out to sea; sometimes lovingly, sometimes longingly, sometimes something else entirely. 

This collection is a reflection of those mixed feelings one experiences with the conclusion of a profound, life-defining experience.
